column3: Midas-open: Station site metadata for uk-mean-wind-obs
Met Office MIDAS Open: UK Land Surface Stations Data
This file contains geographic and temporal information for the stations covered in this version of the uk-mean-wind-obs part of the MIDAS-open collection

The temporal range given here is in relation to the data temporal range available for this station within this dataset and may differ from other dates for the given station in other MIDAS-open datasets
The geographic location relates to the currently recorded station location to 3 decimal places of latitude and longitude
If more precise geographical location information is required please contact the Met Office directly as there may be data management restrictions for stations located on private property
Further station-specific details are given in each station folder in the associated capability files
For fuller station metadata please use the MIDAS station search tool available from the Centre for Environmental Data Analysis
The unique MIDAS identifier for the station

This is a unique ID ascribed to this station within the MIDAS system. It is used across MIDAS as a way to join related data and metadata together where a site may have used different identifiers for different meteorological reports over time.
The filename used for this station
The filename is derived from the station name but replacing spaces with - as necessary
the historic county this station is within

Within MIDAS stations are associated with a set of fixed historic county definitions for the UK and are not amended to reflect modern county boundary changes. For more details refer to the MIDAS documentation.
The station elevation in metres above mean sea level
first year of data associated with this station in this dataset
This relates to the first year of available data within this version of this dataset. The first year may differ for this station within other datasets of Midas-open
last year of data associated with this station in this dataset

This relates to the last year of data associated with this station in this dataset. It does not indicate whether the station is currently operational and the last year may differ for this station within other datasets of Midas-open

The first and last year indicate simply the year of first and last available data in this dataset. They do not indicate the availability of data between those dates or availability of data within other datasets of Midas-open
